SUMMARY:Ion Networking with Cup of Joey
DTSTAMP:20260619T133500Z
DTSTART:20260619T083000Z
DESCRIPTION:What is the purpose of Cup of Joey? It is to create a connected
	 culture of coffee shop-open networking across our region. Every Friday mo
	rning\, you’ll have the opportunity to meet new and expand your current ne
	tworks\, talk about tech\, inspire innovation\, and create community. \nSo
	\, what is the difference between a cup of joe and a Cup of Joe-Y? It is t
	he WHY. It’s not what you do. It is why you do it! \nAt the Ion\, these ar
	e questions that we want to explore with the tech and innovation community
	. So\, show up\, be friendly\, and make new connections. Know your why\, a
	nd we will get to the future together. \nThe future is only a cup away. \n
	Register Here: https://www.cupofjoey.org/\n\nhttps://iondistrict.com/event
	/ion-networking-with-cup-of-joey-34/2026-06-19/\n\nFrom Ion District
URL:https://iondistrict.com/event/ion-networking-with-cup-of-joey-34/2026-0
	6-19/
LOCATION:Ion – Lobby\, 4201 Main St.\, Houston\, 77002\, United States
